Insider Activity


Individual




Hava Klemperer Meretzki



Ms. Hava K. Meretzki is Partner at Meretzki-Tavor and Vice Chairman-National Council at Israel Bar Association. She is on the Board of Directors at Pluristem Therapeutics, Inc.
She received her undergraduate degree from The Hebrew University of Jerusalem.



