Business Summary


Develops stem cell production technologyPluristem Therapeutics, Inc. is a biotechnology company engages in the provision of cell therapy development.It focuses on cell therapies for the treatment of diseases such as muscle injury, acute radiation syndrome, pulmonary arterial hypertension and others.Its products include PLacental eXpanded, PLX-PAD, and PLX-R18.The company was founded by Doron Shorrer on May 11, 2001 and is headquartered in Haifa, Israel.
Number of employees : 169 persons.
 





